#

Herb-Crusted Beef Tenderloin

$75
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

BeefMain CourseGourmetLuxury

Description

A succulent beef tenderloin coated with fresh herbs and garlic, roasted to perfection for a juicy and flavorful main dish.

Ingredients

  • Beef tenderloin: 2 lbs
  • Fresh rosemary: 2 tbsp, chopped
  • Fresh thyme: 2 tbsp, chopped
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Olive oil: 3 tbsp
  • Salt: 1 tbsp
  • Black pepper: 1 tsp
